/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}, {\"begin\": 2047, \"end\": 2060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.040109564217407e-46, \"text\": \"French Police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"disruption\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"the Atlantic, North and East lines\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"a bomb alert\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"the evacuation\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"the Franco-Swiss airport\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"Basel-Mulhouse\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"a routine safety protocol\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the airport resumed operations at midday.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the airport\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"operations\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"midday\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 40-year-old Russian man suspected of planning to sabotage the Games was arrested on Wednesday - however, French police have not publicly stated any link between the Russian national's arrest and the arson attack.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2265, \"end\": 2272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"score\": 0.9998771099381653, \"rank\": 7.134630301903481e-05, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 2358, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource